          <h3 class="hw-pillar-title">Huawei Specialists in Winnipeg</h3>
          <p class="hw-pillar-body">Most Winnipeg repair shops turn Huawei devices away because they can't source parts. We've built dedicated supplier relationships specifically for Huawei and Honor components — allowing us to repair devices that others refuse to touch.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hw-pillar-card">
          <div class="hw-pillar-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 003 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="hw-pillar-title">Hard-to-Find Parts Sourced</h3>
          <p class="hw-pillar-body">Huawei parts availability in Canada is limited due to trade restrictions and reduced market presence. We maintain active supplier relationships for P series, Mate, Nova, and Honor components — contact us to confirm availability for your specific model before visiting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hw-pillar-card">
          <div class="hw-pillar-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="hw-pillar-title">SuperCharge & Fast Charging Experts</h3>
          <p class="hw-pillar-body">Huawei SuperCharge and fast charging failures are a common complaint that most shops misdiagnose. We test the full charging chain — port, cable compatibility, charging IC, and battery — to identify the real cause before recommending any repair.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hw-pillar-card">
          <div class="hw-pillar-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="hw-pillar-title">Warranty on Every Repair</h3>
          <p class="hw-pillar-body">Screen repairs carry a 30-day to lifetime warranty depending on part tier. Battery replacements include a 90-day warranty. All other repairs carry a lifetime warranty on parts and labour — even on hard-to-source Huawei components.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="hw-cost-section" id="pricing">
    <div class="hw-container">
      <div class="hw-section-header">
        <h2 class="hw-section-title">Worried About Repair Cost? You Have Options.</h2>
        <p class="hw-section-subtitle">Most customers use one of these options to lower their repair cost.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hw-cost-grid">
        <div class="hw-cost-card">
          <div class="hw-cost-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="1" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="hw-cost-title">We'll Match Any Local Repair Price</h3>
          <p class="hw-cost-body">Found a lower price at another Winnipeg repair shop? We'll match it — so you don't overpay. No pressure. No hassle.</p>
          <a href="sms:2045009757?body=Hey%20Mobile%20Tech%20Lab!%20I%20want%20a%20better%20price%20on%20a%20repair!" class="hw-price-match-btn">
            Check If We Can Match Your Price
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="hw-cost-card">
          <div class="hw-cost-icon-wrapper">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 0-6.74 2.74L3 8"/><path d="M3 3v5h5"/><path d="M12 7v5l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="hw-cost-title">Lower Your Huawei Repair Cost With a Trade-In</h3>
          <p class="hw-cost-body">Trade in phones, tablets, consoles, or laptops — even broken ones — to reduce today's repair cost.</p>
          <p class="hw-cost-note">Get paid via Cash, E-Transfer, or Store Credit</p>
          <a href="/trade-in" class="hw-trade-in-btn">
            Lower My Huawei Repair Cost &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hw-pricing-context">
        <p class="hw-context-paragraph">Huawei repair costs in Canada are often higher than comparable Samsung or iPhone repairs due to limited parts availability caused by trade restrictions and reduced market presence. Flagship P series and Mate screens use curved OLED panels that are among the most expensive smartphone displays to source and replace.</p>
        <p class="hw-context-paragraph">Many customers are surprised that Huawei parts can cost as much as Apple or Samsung equivalents despite the brand's lower profile in Canada. <a href="https://www.ifixit.com/Search?query=huawei+teardown" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hw-context-link">iFixit's Huawei teardowns</a> show why certain models are more difficult to service — tightly integrated components and proprietary connectors add complexity to even basic repairs.</p>
        <p class="hw-context-paragraph">If the repair cost doesn't make financial sense for your Huawei model's current value, we'll tell you honestly and walk you through alternatives — including trade-in options toward a different device or data recovery if the phone can't be economically repaired. <a href="https://consumer.huawei.com/en/support/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hw-context-link">Huawei support documentation</a> provides additional resources for device troubleshooting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

